    <para id="id7058772">We have already examined these functions in connection with DT filters discussed in previous section.</para>
    <para id="id8429224">A pole at 0 &lt; α &lt; 1 yields a DTFT with large spectral components at low frequencies. As |α| decreases, the unit sample response approaches a unit sample, the DTFT magnitude approaches 1 (0 dB) and the angle approaches 0.</para>
    <figure id="id7444072">
