    </figure>
    <para id="id8975797">A pole at −1 &lt; α &lt; 0 yields a DTFT with large spectral components at high frequencies. As |α| decreases, the unit sample response approaches a unit sample, the DTFT magnitude approaches 1 (0 dB) and the angle approaches 0.</para>
    <para id="id8891218">IV. MODEL OF C/D CONVERTER</para>
