			</m:mrow>
			<m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ { tilde  {X}} \[ m \] } {}</m:annotation>
		</m:semantics>
	</m:math>
</equation><para id="id9530721"> is periodic in m with period N.</para>
    <para id="id8700551">2/ DTFS — periodic unit sample train</para>
    <para id="id6799135">The Fourier series of the periodic unit sample train is</para>
    <para id="element-491"><m:math>
		<m:semantics>
			<m:mrow>
				<m:mstyle fontsize="12pt">
					<m:mrow>
						<m:mrow>
							<m:mover accent="true">
